data.description: This all brick tri-level home sits on a very well kept street in the west end of Elizabethton.  This home features a large living room, spacious eat in kitchen and three bedrooms and two full bathrooms.  This home boasts extensive hardwood and ceramic tile floors and warm neutral colors.  The finished basement features a large den and laundry room.  You will love using the rear deck that overlooks the private level back yard.  Additionally this home features a detached building that has been finished out to make a perfect game room, workout area, or home office. You will find that this home is well worth the asking price for what it offers size, location and quality of construction.  Homes in the west end of Elizabethton at this price point are rare in opportunity so delay to see this great home.  All information and square footage are subject to buyer verification.
